I think the blonde lady's the boss.

262
00:10:00,828 --> 00:10:01,857
Angela?

263
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,762
Who's the oddball now?

264
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,943
I'm warning you,

265
00:10:07,946 --> 00:10:10,162
