310
00:11:50,871 --> 00:11:52,804
Yes. I'm sorry.

311
00:11:54,133 --> 00:11:55,641
Interesting.

312
00:11:55,643 --> 00:11:57,276
What?

313
00:11:57,278 --> 00:11:59,745
